am\": \"negative reactions\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Deleted IPHO FB post BACOLOD, Philippines - Health officials in Iloilo province have stirred controversy by usingFilipino gymnast Carlos Yuloand his two-gold-medal victories in the Paris Olympics to promote their family planning and vasectomy campaign.\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 570, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 339, \"end\": 346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bacolod\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6481808689372754e-16, \"text\": \"BACOLOD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bacolod\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bacolod\"}, {\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 359, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.438564113812492e-18, \"text\": \"Philippines\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Philippines\"}, {\"begin\": 382, \"end\": 388, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\", \"score\": 0.9999987301306523, \"rank\": 1.2697754182934587e-06, \"text\": \"Iloilo\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iloilo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"controversy\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 421}, {\"ngram\": \"usingFilipino gymnast\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 446}, {\"ngram\": \"Carlos Yuloand\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 461}, {\"ngram\": \"his two-gold-medal victories\", \"from\": 462, \"to\": 490}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"their family planning and vasectomy campaign\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 568}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using Yulo as the poster boy for a social media ad campaign, the Iloilo Provincial Health Office (IPHO) offered Ilonggo males a quick and minimally invasive procedure for permanent male contraception, which does not require stitches and has a faster recovery time.\", \"from\": 572, \"t