a\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hurricane_Maria\"}, {\"begin\": 1737, \"end\": 1744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Our_Lady_of_Perpetual_Help\", \"score\": 0.6222965234602363, \"rank\": 0.5683940474298003, \"text\": \"Socorro\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Our_Lady_of_Perpetual_Help\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Our_Lady_of_Perpetual_Help\"}, {\"begin\": 1898, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"score\": 0.9934309784289266, \"rank\": 0.006612458956494214, \"text\": \"Ilonggo\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a statement\", \"from\": 1767, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"the Iloilo-basedDaily Guardian\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1822}, {\"ngram\": \"the campaign\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 1866, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"many negative reactions\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There were also negative interpretations, which we cannot control anymore,\\\" Qui\\u00f1on said.\", \"from\": 1969, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"negative interpretations\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2010}, {\"ngram\": \"Qui\\u00f1on\", \"from\": 2046, \"to\": 2052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the backlash, the Department of Health (DOH) on Wednesday, August 7, gave a nod of approval to the IPHO's brief but controversial vasectomy ad.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the backlash\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2080}, {\"ngram\": \"the Department\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2096}, {\"ngram\": \"Health\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2106}, {\"ngram\": \"(DOH\", \"from\": 2107, \"to\": 2111}, {\"ngram\": \"Wednesday\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 2127, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"a nod\", \"from\": 2142, \"to\": 2147}, {\"ngram\": \"approval\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2159}, {\"ngram\": \"the IPHO's brief but controversial vasectomy ad\", \"from\": 2163, \"to\": 2210}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Health Undersecretary Mary Ann Palermo-Maestral said, \\\"We commend IPHO's creativity for capitalizing on thepopularity of Yulo\\u2026 just to boost its campaign for free-scalpel vasectomy aimed at enticing Ilonggo family men to submit to this minimally invasive family planning procedure.It actually matters nowadays, especially that August is a Family Planning Month.\\\"\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2575, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2235, \"end\": 2239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"score\": 0.7446480677569085, \"rank\": 0.17739977524412054, \"text\": \"Mary\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mary_II_of_England\"}, {\"begin\": 2334, \"end\": 2338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.646169671898221e-15, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 2412, \"end\": 2419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"score\": 0.9934309784289266, \"rank\": 0.006612458956494214, \"text\": \"Ilonggo\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"IPHO's creativity\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"thepopularity\", \"from\": 2317, \"to\": 2330}, {\"ngram\": \"its campaign\", \"from\": 2354, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"free-scalpel vasectomy\", \"from\": 2371, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"this minimally invasive family planning procedure\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2493}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 2540, \"to\": 2546}, {\"ngram\": \"a Family Planning Month\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Maestral said Yulo's popularity might be the perfect \\\"sailing point\\\" for the IPHO to navigate the choppy waters of promoting vasectomies among Ilonggo family men.\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2739, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2591, \"end\": 2595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.646169671898221e-15, \"text\": \"Yulo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carlos_Yulo\"}, {\"begin\": 2720, \"end\": 2727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"score\": 0.9934309784289266, \"rank\": 0.006612458956494214, \"text\": \"Ilonggo\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hiligaynon_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Maestral\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2585}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect \\\"sailing point\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"the IPHO\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2658}, {\"ngram\": \"the choppy waters\", \"from\": 2671, \"to\": 2688}, {\"ngram\": \"vasectomies\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2713}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Wednesday night, the IPHO released an official statement to express its \\\"sincerest apologies for the recent social media ad campaign.\\\"\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wednesday night\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2759}, {\"ngram\": \"the IPHO\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2769}, {\"ngram\": \"an official statement\", \"from\": 2779, \"to\": 2800}, {\"ngram\": \"its \\\"sincerest apologies\", \"from\": 2812, \"to